  "description": "Variation of conditions 3 (Opening hours) and 7 (Hours of external terrace) of planning permission 2020/3385 dated 12/02/2021 for the proposed change of use from a vacant charity shop (Use Class E) into a Pub (Sui generis - drinking establishment) and installation of new shop fronts to both frontages. The variation would allow for extended opening hours between 07.00 and 23.30 hours Monday to Thursday, between 07.00 and 00.30 (the following day) on Fridays and Saturdays and between 07.00 and 23.00 on Sundays and Public Holidays and use of the terrace between 07.00 and 22.00 daily.&nbsp;",
  "title_number": [],
